{"tid":764080,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發現咗最好嘅洗臉時機","createTime":"2018-08-01T16:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T16:09:56.000Z","uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"968b11dca215fd11c5ae3688455031857f0d41c7","tid":764080,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T16:02:31.000Z","msg":"返咗成日工 一返屋企好多人都會成臉油<br />\n有啲人會即刻洗臉 但其實咁樣係殺唔曬啲菌！<br />\n<br />\n因為個時菌嘅數量唔多 你洗走啲油 啲菌可以繼續食啱啱生出嚟嘅油續命<br />\n<br />\n但如果你等到臨訓先洗 個時啲細菌嘅數量已經多咗好多 因為佢地覺得有大量野俾佢地食 所以不斷繁殖<br />\n到你洗走啲油 佢地成堆一齊搶野食 變咗全部都唔夠 <br />\n最後死曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申睇咗工作細胞學返嚟<br />\n<br />\n送返張血小板圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/000228_6614b026f7e378712858a7267ceb5b96.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F000228_6614b026f7e378712858a7267ceb5b96.png&h=a5a8a4a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59251817c1a0f9ae4b5bf16e5dd8dcf9a3471816","tid":764080,"uid":16668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T16:03:37.000Z","msg":"我次次都係沖涼前洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf606812dd0a3416346650c3118ebd27d6bac59","tid":764080,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T16:04:30.000Z","msg":"好想𠝹開個龜頭等d血小板出黎同我接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d629a7bb2a90e8ddce5d899b80018cad12f0e12","tid":764080,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cbf606812dd0a3416346650c3118ebd27d6bac59","tid":764080,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T16:04:30.000Z","msg":"好想𠝹開個龜頭等d血小板出黎同我接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"我幫你 濛狗 come here"},{"pid":"adbb9f041d0271efca52d04efd2df2815d569391","tid":764080,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c